      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BENTLEY FISHER (3) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with four wins and a placing from eight tries. Placed last time (20.15) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 1.5 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. SAMMY'S BEACH (1) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (30.07) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Can feature with the right run. SCOOTIN' SCOOBY (7) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 1.75 lengths 5th at this track (20.18). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Cannot be left out. NORTHERN TIGER (2) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.",
